Block, Brick & Hardscapes


Our vast selection of block, brick and hardscapes products provide quality, strength and style for any residential or commercial building project.
Block Boxley manufactures the area’s largest selection of block shapes and sizes to meet the specifications of even the most complex building projects. We offer gray block, architectural block and fire-rated block as well as permeable and erosion control products--all backed by the region’s largest production capacity and top-notch delivery fleet.
Brick Brick making is a an art form, and Boxley has partnered with some of the finest brick makers in the business to offer you brick and brick pavers in a variety of colors and textures. Rest assured, we have the right brick for your residential or commercial needs.
Hardscapes Boxley hardscapes offers a distinctive selection of pavers, retaining walls and accessories in complementary styles and colors to create the ideal outdoor living space.  We like to call it Outdoor Living…Simplified.
Visit one of our Outdoor Living Showrooms in Roanoke or Lynchburg for inspiration. Contact us at (800) 422-2565 to discuss your residential block, brick or hardscapes project today. 



























