Aggregate


Contractors and road builders count on Boxley aggregate as the foundation for project success. Simply,our crushed stone is cleaner and more consistently sized than any aggregate you’ll find elsewhere. Boxley’s aggregate products are just around the corner from your next residential, commercial or transportation project.  
 

